Message:
In an effort to
rejuvenate our strength,
everyone came to the lake
to play, but...

“I can do the doggy paddle, y’know!
I don’t need your help, you dummy!
You big, blue DUMMY!”

After saying that,
Moddey cried and
fled from my sight.

All she did was
cling to me, though...

...At times like this,
Sophia and Valeriede would
undoubtedly know the best
course of action.

...I truly have
no idea what to do.
